title: One bedroom apartment available Income Restricted
posting_body: ['Summerfield Apartments are located in the beautiful, historic city of Northfield, Minnesota.', 'The community offers an affordable and wide range of apartment layouts, with studios, 1 bedroom, 2 bedroom and 3 bedroom units.', 'Downtown Northfield is just minutes away, with St. Olaf College, Lashbrook Park, John North Park, and Greenvale Park Elementary school within close walking distance.', 'The city of Northfield is also the home of Carleton College.', 'Summerfield Apartments is a quiet apartment community, offering spacious units with detached garages available, air conditioners, onsite caretaker and manager, large balconies or walk-out patios, updated flooring and kitchens, large entertaining areas, and more.', 'The community consists of nine buildings, which provides for a very peaceful interior atmosphere.', 'Laundry facilities are conveniently located on site and there is also a large new playground.', 'Summerfield Apartments has beautiful grounds that are well kept and colorful.', 'Stop by today to see why this peaceful community is right for you!', 'If you would like to apply or get more information, you can go to <URL>', 'You can also call us to schedule a time to view our beautiful property!']
